originalText.text: The worse service ever, unprofessional and uncaring. Filthy vehicles, bad conditions. Lights burnt out. They do not respond to your messages, ever. I do not recommend!! I wish I would’ve looked at these reviews before wasting my time and money. As a new driver with a new license, I honestly only wanted some more experience to build my confidence before purchasing a vehicle of my own. I obtained the experience I was seeking, but their service is literally trash. PLEASE DO NOT BOOK THEM, you will regret it I promise! I would post pictures but I do not want to violate anyone’s privacy. But please do not waste your time. Thank me later

originalText.text: I was trying to rent a car from this company through a car app and got approved. When I tried to call they sent a text saying only sms. I wanted to pick up the car the same day instead the following day. Response time is very slow for them so I waited. Yet trying to catch them before they close I ask again if I’m able to pick up the car. They later on told me they canceled my reservation for the car. I found out via email the reason because I asked if I could pick the car up the same day! Which didn’t make sense and I found it unprofessional. If you run a business how can you not answer questions customers are paying to retrieve the car ? This was my first and last time using this company.
